China to Open National Garment Trade Center
WUHAN , December 24 ( Xinhua ) -- The China Garment Association and China Garment Designers Association plan to establish the nation 's first garment trade center in Wuhan , capital of central China 's Hubei Province .
The center will offer information related to the industry , host exhibitions and distribute high quality garments .
Wuhan , which is located in the heart of China , is one of the major communications hubs .
The city 's prosperous garment industry enjoys annual sales of over six billion yuan .
